movie.overview: A group of friends facing mid-life crises head to the rainforest with the intention of remaking their favorite movie from their youth, only to find themselves in a fight for their lives against natural disasters, giant snakes and violent criminals.
movie.tagline: A comedy so big it'll leave you breathless.
movie.title: Anaconda

results.overview: Holly Golightly is an eccentric New York City playgirl determined to marry a Brazilian millionaire. But when young writer Paul Varjak moves into her apartment building, her past threatens to get in their way.
results.title: Breakfast at Tiffany's

results.original_title: Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home
results.overview: When a huge alien probe enters the galaxy and begins to vaporize Earth's oceans, Kirk and his crew must travel back in time in order to bring back whales and save the planet.
results.title: Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home

results.overview: In the disciplined world of boxing, Fabiana maintains order as a referee, but her life takes an unexpected turn when she decides to adopt Dudu, a troubled 12-year-old boy. To get out of this, she must reconnect with his father, a frustrated actor. While society favors “perfect” mothers, fathers and children, this unlikely trio faces challenges and discovers that family is much more than an ideal model.
results.title: Família em Construção

results.overview: It's good versus evil in the heart of the steamy jungle. Explorer Allison, jungle girl Synda, an evil Baroness and her assistant are all after the much coveted Jewel of Doom. Hey, with a title like that, could anyone survive? Where's the jewel and who's going to end up with it?
results.title: The Jewel of Doom

results.overview: Axel Foley returns to the land of sunshine and palm trees to investigate the near-fatal shooting of police Captain Andrew Bogomil. With the help of Sgt. Taggart and Det. Rosewood, they soon uncover that the shooting is associated with a series of "alphabet" robberies masterminded by a heartless weapons kingpin—and the chase is on.
results.title: Beverly Hills Cop II

results.overview: In the deep south during the 1930s, three escaped convicts search for hidden treasure while a relentless lawman pursues them.
results.title: O Brother, Where Art Thou?

results.overview: A hard-nosed cop reluctantly teams up with a wise-cracking criminal temporarily paroled to him, in order to track down a killer.
results.title: 48 Hrs.

results.overview: In need of funds for research, Dr. Alan Grant accepts a large sum of money to accompany Paul and Amanda Kirby on an aerial tour of the infamous Isla Sorna. It isn't long before all hell breaks loose and the stranded wayfarers must fight for survival as a host of new -- and even more deadly -- dinosaurs try to make snacks of them.
results.title: Jurassic Park III

results.overview: When a childless couple--an ex-con and an ex-cop--decide to help themselves to one of another family's quintuplets, their lives become more complicated than they anticipated.
results.title: Raising Arizona

results.overview: In the winter of 1959, a single mother and her young daughter arrive in a rural French town, where they open an unusual chocolate shop that disrupts the moral fiber of the strictly Catholic townsfolk and mayor.
results.title: Chocolat

results.overview: Frank and Katrin return to Frankfurt to stop the scientist responsible for unleashing the plague of genetically mutated vermin upon the city.
results.title: Scratch: The New Sound of Terror

results.original_title: Mr. Bread & Dr. Cheese in: The Milkman Caper
results.overview: A pair of conmen run into unexpected obstacles during their biggest heist yet.
results.title: Mr. Bread & Dr. Cheese in: The Milkman Caper

results.overview: A demonic force has chosen Freddy Krueger as its portal to the real world. Can Heather Langenkamp play the part of Nancy one last time and trap the evil trying to enter our world?
results.title: New Nightmare

results.overview: Following a bomb scare in the 1960s that locked the Webers into their bomb shelter for 35 years, Adam now ventures forth into Los Angeles to obtain food and supplies for his family, and a non-mutant wife for himself.
results.title: Blast from the Past

results.overview: Restless and ready for an adventure, four suburban bikers leave the safety of their subdivision and head out on the open road. But complications ensue when they cross paths with an intimidating band of New Mexico bikers known as the Del Fuegos.
results.title: Wild Hogs

results.overview: After getting into trouble, a mischievous young man is sent to train under a brutal, but slovenly old beggar, who teaches him the secret of the Drunken Fist.
results.title: Drunken Master

results.original_title: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid
results.overview: A scientific expedition sets out for Borneo to seek a flower called the Blood Orchid, which could grant extended life. Meanwhile, they run afoul of snakes and each other.
results.title: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid

results.overview: A man-cub named Mowgli fostered by wolves. After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan, Mowgli is forced to flee the jungle, by which he embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of the panther, Bagheera and the free-spirited bear, Baloo.
results.title: The Jungle Book

results.overview: Two detectives observe an escaped convict's ex-girlfriend, but complications set in when one of them falls for her.
results.title: Stakeout

results.overview: Deep in the Amazon jungle a group of scientists are on a dangerous mission. When their guide suddenly abandons them, they find themselves in a savage and hostile environment. However, things turn deadly when they find they are in the middle of a hunting ground for a pack of prehistoric predators long thought extinct.
results.title: Extinction
